scene.message:
Heeho-kun: Heeho!{waitkey}Up a floor, I saw a girl{nl}
wearing a weird mask!{clearbox}Hihoko-chan: She was saying{nl}
something real scary~{nl}
like smashing up the school~{clearbox}Heeho-kun: That's bad, heeho!{nl}
If the school gets wrecked,{nl}
what're we supposed to do?{clearbox}Hihoko-chan: Get a job~!{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Work till you sweat~!!{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Support Hihoko forever~!!{clearbox}Heeho-kun: Brrr...{waitkey}{ret}

Hihoko-chan: Heading up?{waitkey}Hmm~{nl}
Well, do your best, I guess~{waitkey}{clearbox}Heeho-kun: Oh right, heeho!{waitkey}Up a floor, I saw a girl{nl}
wearing a weird mask!{clearbox}Hihoko-chan: She was saying{nl}
something real scary~{nl}
like smashing up the school~{clearbox}Heeho-kun: That's bad, heeho!{nl}
If the school gets wrecked,{nl}
what're we supposed to do?{clearbox}Hihoko-chan: Get a job~!{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Work till you sweat~!!{wait_fr:30}{nl}
Support Hihoko forever~!!{clearbox}Heeho-kun: Brrr...{waitkey}{ret}

Heeho-kun: I'll trade you a{nl}
Sealing Tool for that{nl}
Ambrosia you're carrying~{waitkey}{ret}

Heeho-kun: Heeho!{waitkey}Huh?{nl}
You've got something nice~{waitkey}{clearbox}Hihoko-chan: Hiho!!{nl}
She's right,{nl}
she's got Ambrosia~{waitkey}{clearbox}Heeho-kun: Lucky, lucky!{nl}
I want some too!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Hihoko-chan: Hey, hand it{nl}
over! Hand it over~!!{waitkey}{clearbox}Heeho-kun: Um{wait_fr:30}...{wait_fr:30} Miss Hihoko,{waitkey}Teacher said snatching{nl}
things is a no-no, but...{waitkey}{clearbox}Hihoko-chan: Hmm~{nl}
Humans are so difficult~{nl}
So, how about a trade?{waitkey}{clearbox}Heeho-kun: Heeho!!{nl}
I'll trade a Sealing Tool{nl}
for that Ambrosia of yours~{waitkey}{ret}

Hihoko-chan: They say if you{nl}
fuse a Sealing Tool with a{nl}
demon, good things happen~{waitkey}{clearbox}Heeho-kun: I've got five{nl}
Sealing Tools,{nl}
and there are five of you.{waitkey}{clearbox}Hihoko-chan: That's one{nl}
each, by my math.{waitkey}{clearbox}Heeho-kun: Check how much{nl}
Ambrosia you've all got, then{nl}
decide whose Tool to take.{waitkey}{clearbox}Hihoko-chan: Once you decide,{nl}
talk to the human who's{nl}
getting the Sealing Tool.{waitkey}{clearbox}Heeho-kun: If you want your{nl}
own Sealing Tool, come{nl}
talk to us~{waitkey}{clearbox}Hihoko-chan: Phew~{nl}
Talking a lot is tiring~{waitkey}{ret}

Heeho-kun: Now then,{nl}
talk to whoever you want{nl}
to trade with~!!{waitkey}{ret}

Yukino: We've only got so{nl}
much Ambrosia, so we'd{nl}
better choose carefully who{nl}
gets a Sealing Tool.{waitkey}{ret}

Heeho-kun: Heeho!!{nl}
Trading for the{nl}
"Buffalo Beats"~{waitkey}{ret}

Heeho-kun: Heeho!!{nl}
Trading for the{nl}
"Stuffed Deer"~{waitkey}{ret}

Ayase: Hey now~{nl}
Why's it a stuffed thing~!{nl}
I don't want this~!!{waitkey}{ret}

Heeho-kun: Heeho!!{nl}
Trading for the{nl}
"Tortoiseshell Glasses"~{waitkey}{ret}

Nanjo: Th-{wait_fr:30}this is...{waitkey}Aren't these Yamaoka's{nl}
glasses?!{waitkey}{clearbox}Why... why are they{nl}
in a place like this...{nl}
To protect me?{waitkey}Yamaoka...{waitkey}{ret}

Elly: Sealing Tools are{nl}
precious. We should choose{nl}
carefully who receives one.{waitkey}{ret}

Heeho-kun: Heeho!!{nl}
Trading for the{nl}
"Contract of Judgment"~{waitkey}{ret}

Brown: I'm the leader, so{nl}
naturally I've got every{nl}
right to take one, kiddo.{waitkey}{ret}

Heeho-kun: Heeho!!{nl}
Trading for the{nl}
"Victoria Rune"~{waitkey}{ret}
